            If you want to get chat with me, feel free to send an email 😊
            <br>
            <br>
            <a href="https://blog.qianjunakasumi.moe">Visit qianjunakasumi's Blog</a><br>
            Resume at <a href="/resume/" class="px-2 bg-amber-100">HERE</a>
            <br>
            <br>
            Support Language: 简体中文(native) 繁體中文 English 日本語
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6">
            <a href="https://github.com/qianjunakasumi">GitHub</a>
            ・
            <a href="https://huggingface.co/qianjunakasumi">Hugging Face</a>
            ・
            <a href="https://twitter.com/qianjunakasumi">Twitter</a>
            <br>
            mailto: qianjunakasumi@&#123;outlook, gmail&#125;.com
        </p>
    </main>
    <footer class="pl-10 sm:pl-24 text-base qianju flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-20">
            <EngeifudeHorizontal/>
        </div>
        <span class="qianju">© QIANJUNAKASUMI.MOE. {new Date().getFullYear()}</span>
        <a href="https://icp.gov.moe/?keyword=20232034" target="_blank">萌ICP备20232034号</a><br>
    </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
    .qianju-sans {
        font-family: sans-serif;
    }

    .qianju {
        font-family: 'Red Hat Mono Variable', monospace;
    }

    .qwq {
        font-family: serif;
        font-size: 1.06rem;
    }

    footer {
        color: #232129;
    }
</style>
